snippet.title: New Jewish Defence League chapter established in Calgary, Alberta

localized.description:
Don Sharpe is the president of the newly established Calgary chapter of the Jewish Defence League of Canada. He talks to Ezra Levant of TheRebel.media about the purpose of the new group. MORE:  http://www.therebel.media/calgary_chapter_of_jewish_defence_league_canada
